##Several said the epidemic 0224: Beijing for two consecutive days zero growth, Hubei Wuhan continues to be good

I-CAIJING

CAIJING magazine official Wechat. "CAIJING" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was first published in 1998, adhering to the news concept of "independence, exclusiveness and originality" , and is known for authoritative, impartial and professional reporting, it is a must-read publication for policy-makers, researchers and managers in the field of politics and economics.

Most provinces and regions in the country have achieved "zero new" , statistics did not see the resurgence of the epidemic evidence, also did not find that means the resurgence of the epidemic cases

-- Xu Jin, data researcher, Caijing

Photo / CAIJING visual centre

Editor / Ms Cheryl

Today is the second day of the second lunar month. According to the northern rural tradition, from this spring plowing busy start, work in the fields, looking forward to a good year. President Xi made an important speech yesterday, laying out plans to advance the prevention and control of the new crown disease and economic and social development in a coordinated way: He made seven points on the prevention and control of the new crown disease, and once again stressed that Hubei, the Battle of Wuhan and Beijing should do their best to prevent and control the disease; There are eight points about economic and social development, in which "resuming work and resuming production" appears in two sub-headings. Xiao Bian Studies and understands earnestly. Let's take a look at today's numbers.

Cumulative confirmed cases: the total number of cases is expected to control around 80,000

As of 24:00 on February 23, a total of 77,150 new cases of pneumonia had been reported nationwide. The following is a regional trend map.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 1.1

The Red and black lines show that we are in a race with death!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 1.2

The trend line of non-wuhan areas has been clear, it can be seen that: Domestic non-hubei cumulative cases will stay within 13,000 cases, Hubei non-wuhan areas will be within 19,000 cases, Wuhan will be about 48,000 cases. The main variable is whether this new pneumonia will leave no long tail, as SARS did, or whether it will drag out a long tail, as the exponential function suggests (as some experts have recently been concerned) ? Or somewhere in between? The non-hubei data so far are unlikely to pull out a long tail, and if it does, it will be a thin one.

Second, the new cases: the majority of provinces and cities in the country, zero new, Beijing for two days, Hubei Wuhan continued to decline

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 2

The number of new cases in non-hubei areas further decreased to 11 cases, with an average of 0.4 cases per province (urban area) . Shandong and Zhejiang each had one case of a prison outbreak. There are 24 new provinces and cities, accounting for 4 / 5. Beijing for two consecutive days, "zero new" , which is an important factor, dangdangwang cases were followed by isolation observation of 82 people have not yet confirmed cases. According to Xi's plan, the vast low-risk areas should adjust their prevention and control strategies to the input of external prevention and control as soon as possible so as to restore the order of production and life in an all-round way!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 3

Hubei non-wuhan digestion data after adjusting for factors to return to the downward trajectory. Maintain the positive trend.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 4

Wuhan did not live up to expectations, absorbing the "do-all, check-all, rule-all" incremental, and digest the data adjustment factors before the downward trend. According to Xinhua Net on the 23rd, Wuhan is in 3 days of pull a net type big check. 3,502"four categories of personnel" checked, transferred and sent for treatment. They included 559 confirmed cases, 820 suspected cases, 283 fever cases and 1,840 close contacts. Corroborate the statistics.

3. The rate of increase of confirmed cases: The rate of increase in non-hubei areas is further "approaching zero" , and Hubei and Wuhan reconfirm the downward trend

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 5

The growth rate of non-hubei region in China dropped to less than 0.1% . Hubei's non-wuhan region fell to 0.29 per cent and Wuhan to less than 1 per cent. Identify positive trends across the board.

Contact Tracing: Tracking in Hubei and Wuhan has been strengthened

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 6

Hubei this index is still climbing! The recent three-day moving average shows a strong upward trend: The tracking ratio has further increased to about 20. In recent speeches, the central leadership has also re-emphasized the importance of mobilizing the community to make a good flow.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 7

Both Hubei and non-hubei regions continue to decline, meaning that more medical resources, social human resources and isolation space can be released on a large scale to new close contacts tracking isolation.

Five, suspected cases: The increase, the stock is declining

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 8

Hubei (including Wuhan) new suspected cases after 21 appeared a high point for two consecutive days down, to confirm that Wuhan "do everything possible to do everything possible to treat every other" efforts to achieve results.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 9

After the success of Hubei Dragnet investigation, the decline of two consecutive days, confirming the "dragnet screening" results.

Number of patients treated in hospital: continue to release beds on a large scale

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
10

The stock of people treated in hospitals has declined and hospital beds continue to be released on a large scale. The number of people presumed to have been "hospitalized in Hubei" is still falling.

Mortality Rate, cure rate

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 11

The case-fatality rate has risen for three weeks in a row and looks set to continue. There are the time of death and the newly confirmed increase of factors out of SYNC (non-hubei) , there are also the factors of treatment capacity and medical resources (Wuhan) .

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
12

The cure rate is rising even faster. Let's race against death!

8. New discharge and new diagnoses

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 13.1 number of newly discharged and newly diagnosed cases

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 13.2

The number of newly confirmed cases and newly cured cases continued to maintain the scissors gap and core medical resources continued to be released on a large scale.

Summary: Hubei and Wuhan data adjusted to reconfirm the positive trend. Most provinces and regions in the country have achieved "zero new" , statistics did not see the resurgence of the epidemic evidence, also did not find that means the resurgence of the epidemic cases. We can expect that, on the premise of "no slackening and grasping the detailed prevention and control work" , we will "make overall plans for all work related to economic and Social Development" , implement the strategy of precise prevention and control at different levels, and accelerate the resumption of production by enterprises.
